{"tid":513401,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(真心非曲線) 有無iDog睇完蘋果篇文之後眼濕濕!","createTime":"2017-12-29T13:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T05:02:13.000Z","uid":14078,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"67020754a04b3d1ad68d3f511302a3985c01699e","tid":513401,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:01:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone-battery-and-performance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fiphone-battery-and-performance%2F&d=OTeN81HJ7%2BkIrdXV5PEEqQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=734a1bde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone-battery-and-performance/</a><br />\n<br />\n對於我們因應 iPhone 的舊款電池效能表現而採取的應變手法，以及交代相關程序的方式，我們一直聽取各方顧客的意見。有些顧客對 Apple 感到失望，我們謹此真誠致歉。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，我們都致力創造讓顧客喜愛的產品，而令 iPhone 儘可能耐用是其中重要的一環。<br />\n<br />\n這種突如其來的意外關機情況，我們當然認為不能接受。在儘可能避免的情況下，我們不希望用戶錯失任何一通來電、錯過拍照的一刻，或使用 iPhone 的體驗受到任何影響。<br />\n<br />\n我們一直希望顧客的 iPhone 儘可能耐用。Apple 的產品向以耐用見稱，並較其他競爭對手的裝置更長時間保值，我們以此深感自豪。<br />\n<br />\n為了消解顧客的疑慮，答謝他們不離不棄，並重獲每位曾對 Apple 原意有所懷疑的人的信任，我們決定採取以下措施：<br />\n(中略)<br />\n<br />\n對 Apple 來說，顧客的信任就是一切。我們將繼續努力不懈，以爭取並維繫這份信任。只因你的信賴與支持，我們才得以堅守我們熱愛的工作。我們永遠不會忘記，更不會視一切為理所當然。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n篇中文新聞稿響美國出左半日就有, 換電價錢都敲定埋<br />\n然後再出招動之以情<br />\n諗起當年唔知邊間廠搞左幾日都唔出聲,<br />\n再講香港唔屬於全球一部份,<br />\n再睇睇呢篇文, 真係睇到眼濕濕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6536ff849cf156716f248d5d1b1c4764542b6bee","tid":513401,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ccd326fea739b69a3ae491d276bd5d9665a2a6","tid":513401,"uid":131323,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"強逼你食完舊屎之後請你食番粒糖<br />\n然後idog就眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7232f97ae27115f51587cb02b8b2714cce982cf7","tid":513401,"uid":36049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"咸左<br />\n牙曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ead83ef45db30d67cdf52c746a92eee53ce83b3","tid":513401,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:11:04.000Z","msg":"你有幾何聽到人講呢份係我地熱愛既工作<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0be9e1cfcd2c33ae12f38e015fe95d4da9562b","tid":513401,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54bcf7c1952abf65bef244a449aa994304adfbd9","tid":513401,"uid":59976,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2011/12/1112290404141497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2F1112290404141497.jpg&h=bcf8cefa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad5c3bd689999482ba4ced2a0115b9db9f4c5b16","tid":513401,"uid":25619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"射埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3652cabda9baaf0e989dbb76a5457cf8801bda63","tid":513401,"uid":68094,"like":2,"dislike":4,